text: haey avei delke ban bratan aoy puok anak ku kreante chea pheap sabbayrikreay nei chivit lokey bonnaoh . te avei del meannow cheamuoy a l laoh ku la brasaer ning now sthet se th r chea amt samreab banda anak del mean chomnue . haey tow champoh mcheasa robsa puokke te muoy kt del puokke brakl kar touk chetd
